The paper presents a novel generative model that extends Sum-Product Networks (SPNs) and improves their power. This is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning, specifically in the area of probabilistic graphical models. The paper also discusses the tractability of the proposed model, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of theoretical computer science.
